ChangeList.Description: Added the **AzureADBackupAuth** member to the **tokenIssuerType** enumeration.
Deprecated the **riskType** property of the [riskDetection](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/riskdetection?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Deprecated the **eventTypes** property of the [riskUserActivity](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/riskuseractivity?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the **disableResilienceDefaults** property to the [conditionalAccessSessionControls](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalaccesssessioncontrols?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **userRiskLevels** property to the [conditionalAccessConditionSet](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessConditionSet?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the `passwordChange` member to the **conditionalAccessGrantControl** enumeration.
Added the **includeDevices** property to the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **excludeDevices** property to the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Deprecated the **includeDeviceStates** property on the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource
Deprecated the **excludeDeviceStates** property on the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource
Added the **deviceFilter** property to the [conditionalAccessDevices](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalAccessDevices?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **conditionalAccessFilter** type to the [conditionalAccessPolicy](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/conditionalaccesspolicy?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
